{"tid":245954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員辭職率創十五年新高","createTime":"2017-05-16T15:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T07:52:05.000Z","uid":62257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6730929238271910e00dae58e17e3c4e16bb34","tid":245954,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/504865/&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F504865%2F%C2%A0&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a2f1d905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F504865%2F%C2%A0&h=b35a5719\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/504865/&nbsp;</a><br />\n<br />\n公務員去年度辭職率創十五年新高，近六成更是試用期內離任。公務員事務局局長張雲正認為，是勞工市場緊張及失業率偏低，員工選擇多所致，又指大部份的公務員都是自然流失，為確保人手穩定，最快六月開始將現職公務員退休年齡延長最多五年。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n十七萬公務員，上年度超過七千七百人離任，整體流失率 4.7% 。公務員事務局局長張雲正出席立法會委員會時表示，內部分析過大部份是自然流失。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n流失率高另一個原因是多了人辭職， 01/02 年度之後六年，辭職率不多於 0.3% ，直至去年度升至 0.65% ，創十五年新高，六成人未完試用期便辭職。張雲正表示最快六月，按個別部門及職級需要，將現任僱員的退休年齡延長最多五年。"},{"pid":"7a332bbc97116a9d929c93b38ee9a25c2790f31e","tid":245954,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"將現任僱員的退休年齡延長最多五年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心就俾後生上位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b9161104db43ef5e0fbc53520cce0357e7fdcb","tid":245954,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將現任僱員的退休年齡延長最多五年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心就俾後生上位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm